{"tid":811264,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣見親紅巴藍絲都好撚反感","createTime":"2018-09-08T16:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-09T04:32:21.000Z","uid":4826,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1e7d44129423972f9888aceaab13ac9015b9aa0e","tid":811264,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T16:14:49.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味特別係share感情狀況果班<br />\n我舉藍絲為例，成撚日打一大段野叫人比意見呀咁<br />\n我老早已經代入左佢個男性角色黎睇，設想緊多種情境，<br />\n諗住比下意見咁，<br />\n丫！屌佢老味最後利申，或者唔撚知幾多個回覆之後先話自己係絲，<br />\n我屌佢老味真係即時覺得嘥鳩晒我時間睇佢叫春，<br />\n網絡世界已經唔洗你用真名<br />\n連登更加冇PM功能<br />\n如果咁都要掩掩樣樣，<br />\n某程度上我會覺得你地都幾撚唔尊重人，<br />\n更遑論要人地認真聽你地講故事囉！"},{"pid":"83d415a6ba490e25f9cb09796722fd5fb64eeb7a","tid":811264,"uid":198622,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5694e4623beb0c35f27f668dda38d001971e5c26","tid":811264,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:24:18.000Z","msg":"連登太多狗公<br />\n<br />\n小妹唔用藍名會好多人要我留tg"},{"pid":"a5556959e4b88f3b78bd6333aab96815916f72e9","tid":811264,"uid":1914,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:32:30.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"e30e09a4849471dc4b89573e45e0d7d07f05e1d6","tid":811264,"uid":4826,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"5694e4623beb0c35f27f668dda38d001971e5c26","tid":811264,"uid":125168,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T17:24:18.000Z","msg":"連登太多狗公<br />\n<br />\n小妹唔用藍名會好多人要我留tg"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T21:49:40.000Z","msg":"叫你留一定要留？叫你自拍係咪又一定要放埋上黎？"},{"pid":"7cb60a045e3c48fd5012aee94affaf6758919791","tid":811264,"uid":179567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T21:51:06.000Z","msg":"上X登勿認真"},{"pid":"25ea9c088c7d3dcb5ea2f28cb08fb511a37925a7","tid":811264,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"e30e09a4849471dc4b89573e45e0d7d07f05e1d6","tid":811264,"uid":4826,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"p